y quick, I'm more likely to do frequent backups.","distro":"Fedora Linux","karma_down":0,"karma_up":0,"locale":"en_US.UTF-8","rating":80,"reported":0,"review_id":647112,"score":0,"summary":"Simple and reliable","user_display":"Bill Grzanich","user_hash":"5f864d694bc465cdda65a00870b6978e8a232dd8","user_skey":"f9935155aedee6132bfccc8694722937a7c6d112","version":"46.1"},{"app_id":"org.gnome.DejaDup","date_created":1745697284.0,"description":"It backs up to my cloud, external drive and to a file. The only thing I wish it had was an incremental backup, it had one but that went away when it changed over to a different backup type, duplicity to other. Thanks for the great software and yes I have restored twice due to a deletion on my part and a full one due to a crashed disk drive.","distro":"Ubuntu","karma_down":0,"karma_up":0,"locale":"en_US.UTF-8","rating":100,"reported":0,"review_id":646900,"score":0,"summary":"Works great, no problems","user_display":"mike","user_hash":"f784649ef2d2261a885a7574f439377660155380","user_skey":"f9935155aedee6132bfccc8694722937a7c6d112","version":"40.7"},{"app_id":"org.gnome.DejaDup","date_created":1740963565.0,"description":"Backing up to external encrypted SD","distro":"FuriOS","karma_down":0,"karma_up":0,"locale":"en_US.UTF-8","rating":100,"reported":0,"review_id":643061,"score":0,"summary":"Works flawlessly","user_display":"amigamobile","user_hash":"9731c8920bd1f70bb04293e0ae88307f45e2939e","user_skey":"f9935155aedee6132bfccc8694722937a7c6d112","version":"unknown"},{"app_id":"org.gnome.DejaDup","date_created":1739149948.0,"description":"Once in a while, ALL the backup files will be erased. What is the point of doing this?","distro":"Ubuntu","karma_down":0,"karma_up":0,"locale":"en_US.UTF-8","rating":20,"reported":0,"review_id":641786,"score":0,"summary":"Deleted all the previous backups","user_display":"Pascal Oettli","user_hash":"0ff1e16fed52b288a14bed3b5e4712286134f863","user_skey":"f9935155aedee6132bfccc8694722937a7c6d112","version"